subject: I am Mrs. Chantal. I am sendin
body:
I am Mrs. Chantal. I am sending this brief letter to solicit your
partnership to transfer a sum of  5  Million Dollars
Best Regards.
Mrs. Chantal

subject: Re: I am Mrs. Chantal. I am sendin
body:
Dear Mrs. Chantal,

I received your message, but it seems to be incomplete. Could you please provide more details about the transfer of the sum you mentioned?

Best wishes,
James
